HCP-33074

HCP-35329

In HCP v8.2, the HCP software was upgraded to Jetty v9. The upgrade introduces several security enhancements that might impact some deployments:

HCP v8.2

■ HCP no longer supports SSL v1, v2, and v3

protocols.

■ HCP conforms more closely to RFC 7230, and no

longer allows header folding.

